# Harbor Guardians — line-ending policy.
#
# HG-POST-A4-STABILIZATION-01 (H1): the committed, GENERATED browser artifacts
# below are byte-exact compared on every CI run — the `ui:playthrough --check`
# drift guard and the engine build/drift check compare committed bytes to a
# fresh generation, with no CRLF normalization. Pin them to LF so a Windows
# `core.autocrlf=true` checkout cannot introduce false drift (the documented
# Alpha A4 CRLF artifact). This is a TARGETED pin on generated outputs, not a
# repository-wide line-ending or formatting rewrite.
src/ui/shell/seeds.json          text eol=lf
src/ui/shell/playthrough.json    text eol=lf
src/ui/shell/engine/**           text eol=lf
src/save/generated/**            text eol=lf
